metadata.name: Rosa ventus
metadata.description:
Being embodied by 4 hands, which confirms the specificity or even standardity of the combination.

Top – superiority of knowledge;

Hand with a button – a constant struggle with shortcomings

A hand with a needle – is a creative factor having a tendency to remodel, to rebuild.

Hand with katana – peace keeping principle including PAX MENS (peace of mind).
A full artwork description can be found on the website.
